</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Sir_William_Bruce.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6c/Sir_William_Bruce.jpg/220px-Sir_William_Bruce.jpg" width="220" height="258" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6c/Sir_William_Bruce.jpg/330px-Sir_William_Bruce.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6c/Sir_William_Bruce.jpg/440px-Sir_William_Bruce.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
